Modifications (Apache License 2.0, Section 4(b))
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

CentaurAI AIStation has modified the original AionUi work. Notable changes:

  - Rebranding to "CentaurAI AIStation" and the centaurloop.com visual identity
    (warm-domain color theme, brand fonts, 3 core themes).
  - Restructured home sections: "办公助理" (office assistants) and "专家"
    (experts) as separate, parallel sections.
  - Admin-managed model configuration (desktop-managed, WebUI read-only).
  - Per-advisor main-agent + builtin-skill mapping for the agency experts.
  - A LAN distributed client (mDNS auto-discovery + remote connect) so each
    workstation connects to a central admin server.

